subtitleNullable: Dataset of mangas/LN/WN from MyAnimeList.net extracted during December 2020
descriptionNullable:
### Context
This is my second dataset generated by scraping MyAnimeList.net but also, 
> *“Because you always wanted to have another dataset of mangas, here it is.”*


### Content

This dataset contains some data about mangas/light novels/web novels/manhwas from MyAnimeList. The separator for the data is ";".


### Acknowledgements

This data is from MyAnimeList.net, I do not own the data. 


### Inspiration

You can use this dataset however you want, though I suggest to do some clustering on it.
